 <text>
  <front>
   <head>TO MISS H—L—D. 1768.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">TELL me, God of soft desires,</l>
     <l n="2" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Little Cupid, wanton Boy,</l>
     <l n="3" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">How thou kindlest up thy fires!</l>
     <l n="4" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Giving pleasing pain and joy.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">H—l—d's beauty is thy bow,</l>
     <l n="6" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Striking glances are thy darts;</l>
     <l n="7" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Making conquests never slow,</l>
     <l n="8" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Ever gaining conquer'd hearts.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Heaven is seated in her smile,</l>
     <l n="10" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Juno's in her portly air;</l>
     <l n="11" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Not Britania's fav'rite Isle</l>
     <l n="12" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Can produce a Nymph so fair.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">In a desart vast and drear,</l>
     <l n="14" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Where disorder springs around,</l>
     <l n="15" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">If the lovely Fair is there,</l>
     <l n="16" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">'Tis a pleasure-giving ground.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">Oh! my H—l—d! blest with thee,</l>
     <l n="18" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">I'd the raging storm defy,</l>
     <l n="19" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">In thy smiles, I live, am free;</l>
     <l n="20" met="+-|+-|+-|+(-)" line_length="7">When thou frownest, I must die.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
